---
import data from '../data/world.json';
const { origines } = data;
---
<section id="monde" class="py-16 sm:py-24 px-5 sm:px-8 bg-brand-blue relative overflow-hidden">
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none opacity-[0.04]">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" class="w-[500px] h-[500px] sm:w-[700px] sm:h-[700px]" fill="none">
      <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="190" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <ellipse cx="200" cy="200" rx="100" ry="190" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <ellipse cx="200" cy="200" rx="50" ry="190" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <line x1="10" y1="200" x2="390" y2="200" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <ellipse cx="200" cy="200" rx="190" ry="70" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <ellipse cx="200" cy="200" rx="190" ry="130" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="text-brand-amber font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-3">Diversité</p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white font-bold mb-4">
      Nos apprenants viennent du monde entier
    </h2>
    <p class="text-white/55 text-sm max-w-md mx-auto mb-10 sm:mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      Chaque semaine, des hommes et des femmes de toutes origines se retrouvent
      autour d'une langue commune et d'une envie de s'intégrer.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 mb-10 sm:mb-14">
      {origines.map(({ flag, pays }) => (
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 sm:gap-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors rounded-full px-3 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 border border-white/10">
          <span class="text-base sm:text-xl leading-none">{flag}</span>
          <span class="text-white/75 text-xs font-medium">{pays}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-amber/20 rounded-full px-3 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 border border-brand-amber/30">
        <span class="text-brand-amber text-xs font-semibold">et bien d'autres…</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 text-white/40 text-xs sm:text-sm">
      <div class="w-10 sm:w-16 h-px bg-white/20"></div>
      <span>Une passerelle entre les cultures, une porte vers l'avenir</span>
      <div class="w-10 sm:w-16 h-px bg-white/20"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
